To run
docker-compose up --build
docker-compose run --rm tests

curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/simulate \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"src_ip": "192.168.1.10", "dst_ip": "192.168.1.20", "vlan": 10}'

Expected JSON response example:
{
  "log": [
    "âœ… Subnet validation passed",
    "ARP request sent to VLAN 10",
    "ARP reply received: MAC resolved",
    "L2 forwarding via switch S1",
    "L3 routing via router R1",
    "Packet delivered successfully"
  ]
}
